    <title>Hanziyu</title>
    <description><![CDATA[    <small>A satirical language built around pronuncing the written form of 汉字</small>
    <p>This is an entirely joke conlang built around the fundamentally flawed concept of pronouncing chinese characters "just like how they're spelt". I do hope you enjoy, for some reason many people found it and a good chunk of them did.</p>
